channel.title: Terragen - First attempts
channel.description:
Well, I went into Frells topic "looking for new programs" or w\e it is, and finally decided to download Terragen, mainly because it looks sexy as shit. In any case, I've been goofing off for the past hour and made some nice pictures, the last one which I now use as my wallpaper. Still learning the program, but it's pretty nice so far. Go to there website and download the free version of Terragen 2 if you get a chance.
First attempt [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/k4cjyq.jpg[/img]
Another try [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/i56vpx.jpg[/img]
Side view [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/30cn4ld.jpg[/img]
Sunset [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/1g41g4.jpg[/img]
